Class Model2ViewModelAdapter

java.lang.Object
Model2ViewModelAdapter.Model2ViewModelAdapter

      Model2ViewModelAdapter()
      Default constructor for a null adapter instance. This allows the ViewModel to use a placeholder adapter before an operational adapter is set.
